fields.name: Butter Chicken
fields.description: Tandoori chicken marinated in spices and herbs in rich creamy gravy

fields.name: Kebab
fields.description: small cubes of lamb meat cooked on a skewer. One skewer has 5 cubes of meat and 3 skewers for each persons. In total one person will get 15 cubes of lamb meat.

fields.name: Mantu
fields.description: It is made of gow gee wrappers (or you can make your own pastry) with a meat and onion mixture, being steamed and serving with a split pea sauce and garlic yoghurt.

fields.name: Qabuli Palow
fields.description: It consists of steamed rice mixed with raisins, carrots, and lamb. Served for 3 people.

fields.name: Samosa
fields.description: Spicy filling of potatos, peas, coriander and masala in pastrytriangle, plum chutney

fields.name: Pappadams
fields.description: Pappadam is a thin, crisp, round flatbread. It is made from peeled black gram flour, either fried or cooked with dry heat. The flours are made of lentils, chickpeas, rice and tapioca. It is 5 pieces.

fields.name: Onion Bhaji
fields.description: Onion bhaji is a spicy snack made of sliced onions, chili, cilantro, lemon juice, baking powder, salt and turmeric. It is 3 pieces.

fields.name: Carrot Cake
fields.description: Carrot cake with moreish icing and chopped walnuts or pecans.

fields.name: Chocolate Cake
fields.description: Chocolate cake with an airy, light sponge and rich buttercream filling.

fields.name: Vanilla Cake
fields.description: Vanilla cake pairs fluffy vanilla cake layers with a silky vanilla buttercream. Customers mostly order this cake in special occasions like birthdays and parties.

fields.name: Mango Lassi
fields.description: Mango lassi is made from yogurt, milk and mango pulp, and may contain added sugar. It is commonly served cold using sweetened kesar mango pulp mixed with yogurt, cream, or ice cream. It is for 3 people.

fields.name: Spinach Juice
fields.description: Spinach juice is made of apple, spinach, parsley, and lemon plus soothing ginger and cucumber. It is for 3 people.

fields.name: Strawberry Lassi
fields.description: Strawberry Lassi is a classic refreshing drink. It is yogurt based and minimally sweetened, a perfect treat for the whole family. it is more less the same like mango lassi with test of strawberry. It is for 3 people.
